column2: Ek Bata Do Do Bate Char
Ae Zamane Tu Kar Le Sitam Pe Sitam
Tum Ko Mere Dil Ne Pukara
O Shankar Mere Kab Honge Darshan
Jab Pyar Kiya To Marna Kyun
Ae Dil Ab Kahin Le Ja
Tumne Kisi Se Kabhi Pyar Kiya Hai
Chahe Aaj Mujhe Na Pasand Karo
Ham Chhod Chale Hain Mehfil Ko
Jis Dil Mein Basa Tha Pyar Tera
Jo Pyar Tune Mujhko Diya Tha
Mujhko Is Raat Ki Tanhai Mein
Waqt Karta Jo Wafa Aap Hamare Hote
Socha Tha Pyar Hum Na Karenge
Jo Tumko Ho Pasand Wohi Baat Karenge
Koi Jab Tumhara Hriday Tod De
Yun Na Dekho Hamen Baar Baar
Na Na Karte Pyar Tumhi Se
Tu Raat Khadi Thi Chhat Pe
Ek Tha Gul Aur Ek Thi Bulbul
Kisi Pe Dil Agar Aa Jaye To
Dil Jalon Ka Dil Jala Ke
Yeh Mera Dil Yaar Ka Deewana
Haye Mar Gayi O Mar Gayi
Sare Shaher Mein Aap Sa Koi Nahin
Luk Chhip Luk Chhip Jao Na
Agar Dil Hamara Sheeshe Ke Badle
Dekho Re Dekho Band Baje Ke Sath
Hum Bolega To Bologe Ki Bolta Hai
O Daddy Ji Bolo Mera Beta Ji
Peene Wale Ko Peene Ka Bahana
Tere Chehre Mein Woh Jadoo Hai
Akele Hi Akele Chala Hai Kahan
Ek Tu Jo Mila Sari Duniya Mili
Humne Jo Dekhe Sapne Sach Ho Gaya
Jiske Sapne Humen Ros Aate Hai
Mera Padhne Mein Nahin Lage Dil
Ek Tu Na Mila Sari Duniya Mili
Khai Thi Kasam Ek Raat Sanam
Main To Bhool Chali Babul Ka Des
Meri Galiyon Se Logon Ki Yari
Chhoti Si Umar Mein Lag Gaya Rog
Tum Humse Mile Hum Tumse Mile
Pyara Pyara Sama Hai Pyar Kar Le
Ye Samaa Samaa Hai Pyar Ka
Milke Bhi Hum Mil Na Sake
Phool Tumhe Bheja Hai Khat Mein
Kisi Raah Mein Kisi Mod Par
Dilbar Dilbar Kahte Kahte Hua Deewana
Kabhi Raat Din Hum Door The
Hum Ko Mohabbat Ho Gai Hai
